{
  "stem": "25809.2",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The young children are not going to leave their parents, and the parents are not going to leave their children.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So by splitting them up, everybody is going to stay put where they are.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Except my sister, who was a few years older than I was, had found that, through one side door, she could reach a little hallway that would go to a door that went right out to the street.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And she told my father about this.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my father said, well, get out and go to our prearranged place, where we were going to meet if anything like this would-- would happen.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That was the carpenter, Thyssen, who had built the double wall, who was our safe house if we ever would-- if ever anything would happen.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "T-H-Y-S-S-E-N.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know his first name, because he was always referred to as Mr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Thyssen.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] You know the formalities in Holland.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We don't work on first name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anyhow, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Ronny just-- literally just walked out of that side door and disappeared.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The next day, I went to my father, and said, I don't where Ronny is.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She's gone.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my father said, that's good.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's good.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But I hadn't-- didn't know how she had gotten away.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "People were watching us, and I was afraid to do almost anything, you might say.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And one day I got very scared because I was-- I moved a standing electrical lamp.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the electrical lamp was connected to the electricity, and there was a short circuit.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And the steel bar-- and I almost electrocuted myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Fortunately, I walked backwards.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And as I walked backwards, by the impact, I pulled the connection out of the-- out of the-- out of the wall.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
